title: Mill Brook Ridge
text: Mill Brook Ridge is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> located in the <a href="Catskill%20Mountains">Catskill Mountains</a> of <a href="New%20York%20%28state%29">New York</a> south of <a href="Arkville%2C%20New%20York">Arkville</a>. Mill Brook Ridge is located north of <a href="Woodpecker%20Ridge">Woodpecker Ridge</a>.
